# Ralph reviewer: one senior-review pass at :13 and :43 past every hour.
# Install with:  crontab -e   (paste the line below)
# Appends to ~/review-board.log. SHADOW mode by default (no auto-merge).
13,43 * * * * /home/div/.local/bin/review-board

# Ralph worker: autonomous pickup, SCOPED TO REP-SHEET + SKILLS (work-board's jq filter).
# Runs at :00 and :30. Appends to ~/work-board.log. Every Ready-for-Agent or
# Changes-Requested card on rep-sheet or skills is a live trigger; widen the jq filter
# or slow the schedule as needed.
0,30 * * * * /home/div/.local/bin/work-board
